  <brief_title>Utilization of Human Papillomavirus (HPV) Vaccine Among Young Men Who Have Sex With Men (MSM) and Parents of Boys (Aged 9 to 18 Years)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Survey Study of the Awareness, Acceptance, and Barriers to Utilization of Human Papillomavirus (HPV) Vaccine Among Young Men Who Have Sex With Men (MSM) and Parents of Boys (Aged 9 to 18 Years)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
